      "rationale": "Validation experiments used the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry (identical to COU geometry), porcine blood as working fluid, and the same 5 flow-speed operating points defined in the COU. No geometric or operating condition extrapolation is required between validation and COU application."
    },
