      "rationale": "The Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law hemolysis model is the predominant model used in FDA-cited pump hemolysis literature. Formal model form uncertainty quantification is not required at MRL 2. Literature precedent (Fraser et al. 2012, Taskin et al. 2012) supports model form selection for this class of centrifugal pump."
